<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-5"><a href="#Meanings_of_the_strict_mass.E2.80.93energy_equivalence_formula.2C_E.C2.A0.3D.C2.A0mc.C2.B2"><span class="tocnumber">4</span> <span class="toctext">Meanings of the strict mass–energy equivalence formula, <i>E&#160;=&#160;mc</i>²</span></a>
